title: Leslie Odom Jr. / Swine Flu
description: Sean learns why you should never mix Sudafed and Codeine. The multi-talented actor, Leslie Odom Jr. (One Night in Miami, Hamilton), joins us to discuss his experience with Swine Flu.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
